2%3Esupplements%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Medical%20Association%2C%20and%20the%20market%20is%20set%20to%20make%20about%20%24308%20billion%20worldwide%20by%202028%2C%20according%20to%20Statista.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20based%20in%20London%20shared%20the%20supplements%20he%20takes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20he%20avoids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223253%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luke%20Worthington%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660595ef3f923f7dab0225e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorthington%20is%20an%20active%20person%20both%20in%20his%20job%20and%20leisure%20time.%3Cp%3ELuke%20Worthington%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWorthington%20has%20stopped%20taking%20pre-workout%20supplements.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20younger%20man%2C%20Worthington%20took%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbenefits-of-pre-workout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-workout%20supplements%20%3C%2Fa%3Edesigned%20to%20give%20you%20more%20energy%20to%20exercise.%20However%2C%20he%20realized%20they%20are%20mostly%20large%20doses%20of%20caffeine%20with%20a%20few%20other%20added%20ingredients%2C%20such%20as%20amino%20acids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20large%20body%20of%20evidence%20demonstrating%20caffeine's%20effectiveness%20as%20a%20performance%20enhancer%2C%20so%20these%20supplements%20do%20'work'%20in%20that%20you%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20able%20to%20work%20harder%20during%20your%20workout%20when%20you%20take%20them%20vs%20when%20you%20don't%2C%26quot%3B%20Worthington%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20backfired%20for%20him.%20The%20young%20Worthington%20was%20always%20pushing%20himself%20to%20work%20as%20hard%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20he%20now%20knows%20that%20training%20with%20sustainability%20in%20mind%20is%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20if%20I%20don't%20feel%20'up'%20for%20a%20particular%20workout%2C%20I%20work%20at%20a%20lower%20intensity%2C%20focusing%20more%20on%20technique%20and%20skill%2C%20rather%20than%20reaching%20for%20caffeine%2C%26quot%3B%20Worthington%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWorthington%20takes%20five%20supplements%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVitamin%20D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20take%20vitamin%20D%20daily%20between%20October%20and%20April%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20UK%20the%20sun's%20rays%20are%20simply%20not%20strong%20enough%20during%20these%20months%20to%20naturally%20provide%20the%20vitamin%20D%20that%20we%20need.%20Vitamin%20D%20is%20vital%20for%20bone%20health%2C%20mood%2C%20and%20immunity%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegistered%20nutritionist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverdoing-vitamin-supplements-could-cause-diarrhea-hair-loss-expert-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERhiannon%20Lambert%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20residents%20of%20the%20UK%20and%20countries%20with%20similar%20levels%20of%20sunlight%20should%20supplement%20with%20vitamin%20D%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20winter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtein%20powder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lead%20a%20very%20active%20life%20with%20an%20active%20job%2C%20and%20I%20aim%20to%20do%20weight%20lifting%20or%20martial%20arts%20every%20day.%20I'm%20also%20quite%20a%20large%20person%20with%20a%20body%20weight%20of%20220%20pounds%2C%20so%20my%20daily%20protein%20requirement%20is%20between%20200%20and%20250%20grams.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20consume%20enough%20through%20whole%20foods%20alone%2C%20so%20whey%20protein%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20boost%20my%20intake%20without%20excessive%20additional%20calories%2C%26quot%3B%20Worthington%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsuming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-protein-daily-diet-to-lose-body-fat-keep-muscle-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenough%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20essential%20for%20overall%20health%2C%20but%20particularly%20important%20for%20muscle%20maintenance%20and%20recovery%20after%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFish%20oils%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOmega-3%20fatty%20acids%20are%20vital%20for%20cardiovascular%20health%20and%20also%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20joint%20health%20and%20brain%20function.%20Omega%203%20is%20what%20we%20call%20an%20essential%20fatty%20acid%2C%20which%20means%20we%20have%20to%20obtain%20it%20through%20diet%2C%26quot%3B%20Worthington%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20eat%20oily%20fish%20such%20as%20salmon%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20week%2C%20however%2C%20that%20isn't%20always%20possible%20with%20a%20very%20busy%20schedule.%20Fish%20oils%20are%20relatively%20inexpensive%20and%20a%20good%20way%20of%20ensuring%20you%20get%20your%20intake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20well%20established%20that%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids%20are%20good%20for%20heart%20health%3A%20they%20slow%20the%20build-up%20of%20plaque%20(which%20blocks%20the%20arteries)%2C%20lower%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20reduce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fhow-to-lower-triglycerides%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etriglycerides%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20type%20of%20fat%20in%20the%20blood.%20However%2C%20research%20is%20mixed%20on%20whether%20fish%20oil%20supplements%20provide%20the%20same%20benefits%20as%20eating%20oily%20fish%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollagen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20turning%2040%20I%20have%20been%20supplementing%20daily%20with%20collagen%20peptides%2C%20mostly%20for%20joint%20health%20to%20offset%20the%20inevitable%20wear%20and%20tear%20connective%20tissues%20experience%20as%20we%20get%20older%2C%20but%20also%20(being%20totally%20honest!)%20I%20have%20enjoyed%20the%20benefit%20of%20better%20skin%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Worthington%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvidence%20around%20collagen%20supplementation%20is%20still%20emerging.%20There%20is%20some%20research%20to%20suggest%20it%20may%20benefit%20our%20connective%20tissue%20(ligaments%2C%20tendons%2C%20cartilage)%2C%20as%20dietitian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollagen-benefits-improves-bone-health-reduces-joint-pain-injury-risk-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESophie%20Medlin%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20BI.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-collagen-supplements-help-with-anti-aging-dermatologists-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskin%20and%20hair%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20data%20isn't%20conclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreens%20powder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20often%20a%20hotly%20debated%20topic%2C%20and%20whilst%20it%20is%20true%20that%20you%20can%20get%20all%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20greens%20supplement%20by%20simply%20eating%20more%20greens%2C%20sometimes%20that%20isn't%20always%20possible%2C%20even%20for%20those%20of%20us%20for%20whom%20health%20and%20fitness%20is%20our%20profession%2C%26quot%3B%20Worthington%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20take%20a%20greens%20supplement%20first%20thing%20every%20morning%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20nutritional%20'insurance'%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20micronutrient%20needs%20are%20met%20even%20if%20that%20particular%20day%20I%20can't%20get%20the%20fresh%20fruit%20and%20veg%20that%20I%20may%20want%20or%20intend%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegistered%20dietitian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreens-powder-trend-tiktok-waste-of-money-dietician-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKatey%20Davidson%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20greens%20powders%20may%20be%20helpful%20for%20some%2C%20they're%20unnecessary%20for%20most%20people%20who%20eat%20a%20balanced%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luke%20Worthington%20training%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e6f557e235c18638c3e6e63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELuke%20Worthington%20is%20a%20personal%20trainer%20to%20the%20stars.%20%3Cp%3ELuke%20Worthington%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWorthington%20never%20takes%20supplements%20that%20claim%20to%20'hack'%20metabolism%20or%20blood%20sugar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorthington%20said%20he%20would%20never%20take%20any%20supplement%20that%20claims%20to%20%26quot%3Bhack%26quot%3B%20your%20metabolism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20just%20snake%20oil%2C%20and%20basing%20fairly%20wild%20claims%20on%20small%20studies%20that%20have%20shown%20tiny%20increases%20in%20thermogenesis%20(essentially%20body%20temperature)%20from%20ingredients%20such%20as%20cayenne%20pepper%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20evidence%20at%20all%20that%20super%20high%20doses%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20ingredient%20have%20any%20impact%20at%20all%20on%20metabolic%20rate%2C%20or%20on%20body%20composition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorthington%20also%20avoids%20anything%20that%20claims%20to%20counteract%20blood%20sugar%20spikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-weight-loss-12-pounds-spiking-increasing-blood-sugar-levels-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20sugar%20spikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20perfectly%20natural%20and%20essential%20part%20of%20metabolism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWanting%20to%20eat%20food%20without%20elevating%20blood%20sugar%20is%20a%20little%20like%20hoping%20to%20exercise%20without%20elevating%20heart%20rate%20and%20blood%20pressure.%20They%20are%20essential%20and%20natural%20responses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20continuous%20glucose%20monitors%20can%20be%20beneficial%20for%20diabetic%20and%20pre-diabetic%20people%2C%20otherwise%20healthy%20people%20don't%20need%20them.%20Worthington%20thinks%20supplements%20claiming%20to%20reduce%20or%20eliminate%20blood%20sugar%20spikes%20are%20another%20way%20marketing%20departments%20try%20to%20convince%20people%20to%20buy%20something%20for%20a%20problem%20that%20doesn't%20really%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdakota-johnson-celebrity-personal-trainer-supplements-takes-avoids-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711877821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6605963d3f923f7dab0226d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdakota-johnson-celebrity-personal-trainer-supplements-takes-avoids-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dakota%20Johnson's%20personal%20trainer%20used%20to%20take%20a%20pre-workout%20supplement%20but%20has%20since%20realized%20that%20they%20stopped%20him%20from%20listening%20to%20his%20body.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdakota-johnson-celebrity-personal-trainer-supplements-takes-avoids-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Housing%20sales%20in%20Gurugram%20down%2012%25%20during%20Jan-Mar%3B%20up%2019%25%20in%20Noida%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711877238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F28%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1682678597-9825.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fhousing-sales-in-gurugram-down-12-during-jan-mar-up-19-in-noida-report-124033100225_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20data%2C%20housing%20sales%20in%20Greater%20No