r%20%244%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-secret-stock-sales-gm-q3-portfolio-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexited%20the%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarra%20told%20Buffett%20about%20all%20the%20new%20features%20he%20could%20get%20in%20a%20new%20car%2C%20and%20the%20investor%20was%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20Cadillac%20and%20a%20matching%20hat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Berkshire%20CEO%20dispatched%20his%20daughter%2C%20Susie%20Buffett%2C%20to%20scope%20out%20a%20local%20Cadillac%20dealer.%20The%20saleswoman%20didn't%20know%20the%20car%20was%20for%20Warren%20Buffett%20until%20after%20the%20sale%20was%20made.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20enquiring%20about%20the%20driver's%20habits%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-diet-mcdonalds-coke-junk-food-soda-ice-cream-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20saleswoman%20steered%20her%20toward%20buying%20the%20roomier%20XTS%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20CTS%20that%20Barra%20had%20recommended.%20GM%20shared%20the%20story%20on%20its%20now-defunct%20FastLane%20blog%3B%20an%20archived%20copy%20can%20be%20accessed%20via%20the%20Wayback%20Machine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20140718150851%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Ffastlane.gm.com%2F2014%2F07%2F15%2Fwarren-buffet-praises-cadillac-dealer-experience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auto%20giant%20also%20published%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20140718150856%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Ffastlane.gm.com%2F2014%2F07%2F15%2Fwarren-buffetts-secret-shopper-stuns-saleswoman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20sharing%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20saleswoman%2C%20Madison%20Willers.%20She'd%20assumed%20Buffett's%20daughter%20was%20a%20secret%20shopper%20there%20to%20test%20her%20product%20knowledge%2C%20and%20was%20thrilled%20when%20she%20returned%20and%20revealed%20her%20father%20was%20the%20mystery%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Buffett%20requested%20that%20I%20personally%20deliver%20his%20XTS%20so%20that%20he%20could%20say%20hello%20after%20all%20the%20time%20that%20had%20passed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWillers%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bthrilled%20and%20humbled%26quot%3B%20that%20Buffett%20remembered%20her%2C%20and%20she'd%20%26quot%3Balways%20been%20impressed%20by%20his%20kindness%20and%20humility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Willers%20dropped%20off%20the%20car%2C%20she%20brought%20a%20Cadillac%20hat%20to%20give%20the%20billionaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20seemed%20just%20as%20excited%20about%20the%20hat%20as%20he%20was%20about%20the%20car%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20tells%20you%20all%20that%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-warren-buffett-spends-money-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuffett's%20thank%20you%20letter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20was%20so%20pleased%20by%20the%20whole%20experience%20that%20he%20penned%20a%20letter%20to%20Barra%20praising%20Willers%20for%20doing%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrific%20job.%26quot%3B%20He%20included%20a%20photo%20of%20him%20and%20Willers%20standing%20next%20to%20his%20new%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSusie%20said%20that%20her%20dad's%20'car-guy%20friend'%20(that's%20you)%20said%20he%20should%20buy%20a%20CTS%2C%20but%20Madison%2C%20then%2023%2C%20said%20the%20XTS%20would%20be%20more%20appropriate%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20wrote%20to%20Barra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20reflects%20an%20evaluation%20on%20her%20part%20that%20from%20Susie's%20description%20I%20must%20be%20hopelessly%20over-the-hi