e%20experience.%20It%20drove%20well%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20issues%20with%20it%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20feel%20Jaguar%20was%20really%20invested%20in%20it.%20They%20put%20out%20the%20car%20and%20there%20weren't%20a%20lot%20of%20updates%20to%20it%20after%20that%2C%20so%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20to%20get%20a%20different%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-fsr-electric-suv-ocean-range-price-photos-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFisker%20Ocean%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20great%20option%2C%20based%20on%20the%20price%20and%20a%20nice%20marketing%20message%20around%20the%20sustainability%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20I%20also%20thought%20their%20involvement%20with%20Magna%20and%20the%20way%20the%20business%20model%20was%20set%20up%20indicated%20that%20the%20vehicle%20quality%20was%20going%20to%20be%20good.%20I%20never%20looked%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-history-founders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I%20was%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20had%20concerns%20about%20their%20build%20quality%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20on%20the%20Fisker%20waitlist%20for%20about%20a%20year%20before%20I%20got%20the%20car.%20It%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20my%20daily%20driver%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20possible%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edue%20to%20all%20the%20issues%20I%20had%20with%20it.%20It%20was%20a%20nightmare%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20Fisker's%20response%20has%20been%20horrible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20vehicle%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20October.%20From%20the%20second%20day%20of%20driving%20the%20car%2C%20I%20started%20having%20issues%20with%20the%20Advanced%20Driver-Assistant%20System%20(ADAS)%2C%20a%20system%20designed%20to%20use%20sensors%20and%20cameras%20on%20the%20car%20to%20improve%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20vehicle%20and%20detect%20issues%20a%20human%20might%20miss.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMultiple%20warnings%20would%20come%20up%2C%20such%20as%20regenerative%20braking%2C%20front%20collision%2C%20front%20cameras%2C%20side%20sensors%2C%20and%20daytime%20running%20lights%20being%20unavailable.%20I'd%20see%20a%20combination%20of%20any%20one%20of%20those%20when%20I%20was%20driving%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reported%20the%20ADAS%20issues%20to%20Fisker%20and%20I%20didn't%20feel%20they%20were%20very%20responsive.%20I%20emailed%20them%20at%20least%20nine%20different%20times%20about%20the%20issue%20and%20no%20one%20came%20out%20to%20fix%20it.%20A%20tech%20came%20out%20for%20a%20different%20issue%20and%20when%20I%20told%20him%20about%20it%20he%20said%20they'd%20fix%20the%20ADAS%20issues%20in%20a%20larger%20software%20update%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20last%20November%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20they%20said%20that%20for%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20car%20was%20stuck%20in%20my%20driveway%20for%209%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20six%20months%20that%20I%20owned%20my%20Fisker%2C%20it%20was%20serviced%20four%20times%20by%20a%20technician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20response%20when%20I%20reached%20out%20for%20service%20was%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20car%20was%20dead%20in%20my%20driveway%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20several%20times%20before%20they%20responded.%20I%20finally%20got%20them%20to%20come%20out%20by%20commenting%20on%20a%20public%20post%20on%20their%20Instagram%20account%20%E2%80%94%20that%20got%20a%20quick%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20three%20or%20four%20weeks%20into%20owning%20it%2C%20Fisker%20did%20an%20over-the-air%20update.%20The%20morning%20after%20the%20update%20I%20could%20hear%20the%20alarm%20going%20off%20in%20the%20car.%20It%20went%20off%20for%20probably%2030%20minutes%20and%20then%20the%2012-volt%20battery%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reported%20the%20issue%20to%20Fisker%20right%20away%20and%20I%20struggled%20to%20get%20them%20to%20come%20out%20and%20service%20it.%20They%20initially%20wouldn't%20tell%20me%20when%20they'd%20come%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20eventually%20reached%20out%20to%20them%20on%20Instagram%20and%20the%20response%20was%3A%20%26quot%3BYour%20case%20has%20been%20escalated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20them%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20car%20is%20not%20drivable.%20It's%20stuck%20in%20my%20driveway.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20the%2012-volt%20dies%2C%20you%20can't%20even%20get%20into%20the%20car%2C%20you%20can't%20start%20it%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20really%20do%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%202023%20Fisker%20Ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a340de58babf00188d55b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202023%20Fisker%20Ocean.%3Cp%3EFisker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20Fisker%20sent%20out%20a%20roadside%20assistance%20guy%20to%20jump%20the%20car%20and%20the%20car%20wouldn't%20jump.%20The%20guy%20Fisker%20initially%20sent%20said%20he%20wasn't%20qualified%20to%20replace%20the%20battery%2C%20so%20the%20car%20was%20in%20my%20driveway%20for%20nine%20days%20before%20they%20got%20a%20technician%20out%20who%20could%20replace%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20wasn't%20the%20only%20issue%20the%20technician%20fixed.%20He%20also%20replaced%20my%20seat%20sensor.%20It'd%20been%20getting%20to%20the%20point%20where%20almost%20every%20day%20I%20had%20to%20move%20around%20in%20the%20seat%20in%20order%20to%20get%20the%20sensor%20to%20register%20that%20I%20was%20sitting%20in%20it%20so%20I%20could%20get%20it%20to%20drive.%20I'd%20heard%20stories%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiskerati.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFiskerati%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%20getting%20stuck%20in%20drive-thrus%20or%20car%20washes%20because%20they'd%20put%20their%20Fisker%20Ocean%20into%20park%20and%20then%20when%20they'd%20try%20to%20pull%20forward%20it%20wouldn't%20register%20them%20in%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20into%20the%20car%20was%20another%20issue.%20Fisker's%20key%20fob%20can%20be%20pretty%20finicky.%20You%20couldn't%20unlock%20or%20lock%20the%20car%20from%20certain%20angles%20or%20distances.%20I%20asked%20the%20tech%20who%20fixed%20my%2012-volt%20battery%20and%20he%20said%20the%20best%20way%20to%20fix%20it%20was%20to%20just%20buy%20another%20key%20fob%20battery.%20That%20worked%20for%20me%20but%20it%20meant%20I%20had%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20battery%20for%20the%20fob%20about%20once%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20wanted%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it%20before%20it%20could%20lose%20any%20more%20value%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20like%20there%20was%20a%20deadline%20looming%20over%20my%20head%20for%20when%20I%20needed%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20car%2C%20between%20YouTuber%20Marques%20Brownlee's%20review%20and%20reports%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-18%2Ffisker-stops-production-and-warns-it-may-need-to-seek-bankruptcy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20possible%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20I%20got%20estimates%20from%20Carmax%20and%20Carvana.%20One%20was%20%2458%2C000%20and%20the%20other%20was%20about%20%2460%2C000.%20I'd%20paid%20over%20%2472%2C000%20for%20the%20car%20only%20three%20months%20prior%20and%20I%20initially%20didn't%20want%20to%20take%20that%20much%20of%20a%20haircut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20March%2C%20I%20got%20estimates%20of%20%2444%2C000%20and%20%2447%2C000.%20I%20was%20very%20concerned%20about%20the%20value%20of%20that%20car%20and%20what%20could%20happen%20to%20any%20type%20of%20service%20requests%20or%20if%20I%20ran%20into%20more%20problems%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20Fisker%20has%20really%20hosed%20their%20buyers.%20It%20felt%20like%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way%20they%20said%20things%20were%20going%20to%20get%20better%20with%20the%20next%20update%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20like%20delay%20after%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20try%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20car%20and%20sell%20it%20before%20its%20value%20could%20sink%20any%20further.%20I%20sold%20it%20for%20%2448%2C000%20later%20in%20March%20at%20about%20a%20%2424%2C000%20loss.%20My%20car%20had%20less%20than%201%2C800%20miles%20on%20it%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20the%20issues%20noted%20have%20been%20resolved%20with%20the%20latest%202.0%20software%20update%20that%20has%20rolled%20out%20to%20customer%20vehicles%20these%20past%20couple%20of%20weeks.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20said%20that%20the%20new%20update%20would%20address%20problems%20the%20owner%20experienced%20like%20the%20ADAS%20and%20key%20fob%20issues%2C%20and%20that%20past%20updates%20addressed%20issues%20related%20to%20the%2012-volt%20battery%20dying%20and%20the%20car%20alarm%20going%20off.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20company%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20owner's%20issues%20with%20customer%20service%2C%20but%20said%20it%20has%20an%20%26quot%3Bestablished%20escalation%20process%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20service%20process.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20similar%20to%20what%20a%20customer%20of%20any%20vehicle%20brand%20would%20experience%2C%20as%20oftentimes%20vehicles%20cannot%20be%20fully%20serviced%20by%20mobile%20technicians%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERegarding%20the%20owner's%20seat-sensor%20issue%2C%20the%20Fisker%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20seat%20sensor%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Broutine%20fix%20for%20some%20early%20vehicles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-ocean-owner-experience-