We%20have%20seen%20the%20media%20reports%20on%20Indian%20nationals%20stuck%20in%20Cambodia.%20Our%20Embassy%20in%20Cambodia%20has%20been%20promptly%20responding%20to%20complaints%20from%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20were%20lured%20with%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20that%20country%20but%20were%20forced%20to%20undertake%20illegal%20cyber%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20around%20250%20Indians%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Brescued%20and%20repatriated%26quot%3B%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20those%20trapped%20in%20Cambodia%20were%20forced%20to%20scam%20people%20back%20home%20in%20India%20and%20extort%20money%20by%20posing%20as%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20and%20telling%20the%20potential%20victims%20that%20suspicious%20things%20were%20found%20in%20parcels%20shipped%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20became%20aware%20of%20this%20massive%20scam%20late%20last%20year%20when%20a%20senior%20central%20government%20employee%20claimed%20he%20was%20defrauded%20of%20over%20Rs%2067%20lakh%20and%20filed%20a%20complaint.%20Odisha's%20Rourkela%20Police%20busted%20a%20cyber-crime%20syndicate%20on%20December%2030%20and%20arrested%20eight%20people%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20moving%20people%20to%20Cambodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20arrested%20eight%20persons%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20have%20prima%20facie%20evidence%20against%20multiple%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20scam.%20We%20issued%20Look%20Out%20Circulars%20against%2016%2C%20following%20which%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Immigration%20detained%20two%20men%20-%20Harish%20Kurapati%20and%20Naga%20Venkata%20Sowjanya%20Kurapati%20-%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20airport%20after%20they%20landed%20from%20Cambodia%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20officer%20said%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F5000-indians-in-cambodia-forced-into-cyber-scams-mha-takes-note-9239156%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Modus%20Operandi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStephen%2C%20one%20of%20the%20men%20rescued%20from%20Cambodia%2C%20has%20an%20ITI%20degree.%20When%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20struck%2C%20he%20did%20some%20computer%20courses%2C%20he%20told%20The%20Indian%20Express%2C%20detailing%20the%20racket's%20modus%20operandi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20agent%20in%20Mangaluru%20offered%20me%20a%20data%20entry%20job%20in%20Cambodia.%20There%20were%20three%20of%20us%2C%20including%20one%20Babu%20Rao%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20At%20the%20immigration%2C%20the%20agent%20said%20we%20were%20going%20on%20a%20tourist%20visa%2C%20which%20made%20me%20suspicious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20were%20taken%20to%20an%20office%20in%20Cambodia%20where%20they%20were%20interviewed%2C%20Stephen%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20only%20two%20of%20them%20could%20clear%20it.%20The%20boss%20was%20Chinese%2C%20while%20a%20Malaysian%20helped%20translate%20for%20them%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20tested%20our%20typing%20speed%20among%20other%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20only%20later%20that%20we%20found%20out%20that%20our%20job%20was%20to%20look%20for%20profiles%20on%20Facebook%20and%20identify%20people%20who%20can%20be%20scammed.%20The%20team%20was%20Chinese%2C%20but%20a%20Malaysian%20translated%20the%20instructions%20to%20English%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Day%20In%20The%20Lives%20Of%20Cyber%20Slaves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForced%20to%20pose%20as%20women%20with%20fake%20social%20media%20profiles%20and%20fake%20photos%2C%20the%20men%20were%20given%20daily%20targets%2C%20and%20punishment%20for%20not%20meeting%20them.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20recruits%20would%20spend%20their%20days%20in%20a%20country%20they%20were%20lured%20to%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bpromise%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20better%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bcyber%20slaves%26quot%3B%20would%20go%20without%20food%20and%20rest%20if%20they%20failed%20to%20meet%20their%20daily%20targets%2C%20the%20Express%20report%20quoted%20Stephen%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20create%20fake%20social%20media%20profiles%20with%20pictures%20of%20women%20sourced%20from%20different%20platforms.%20We%20were%20told%20to%20be%20careful%20while%20picking%20the%20photos%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Indian%20woman%26quot%3B%20would%20trap%20someone%20in%20the%20north%20to%20avoid%20raising%20any%20suspicion.%20We%20had%20targets%20and%20if%20we%20didn't%20meet%20them%2C%20we%20would%20not%20get%20food%20or%20be%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20our%20rooms.%20Finally%2C%20after%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%2C%20I%20contacted%20my%20family%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20some%20local%20politicians%2C%20they%20managed%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20Embassy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Were%20The%20Indians%20Scammed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20took%20the%20men%2C%20or%20the%20potential%20scammers%2C%20to%20Cambodia%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20jobs%2C%20Rourkela's%20police%20official%20Upasana%20Padhi%20told%20The%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20there%2C%20the%20men%20were%20made%20to%20join%20the%20companies%20that%20indulged%20in%20defrauding%20people%2C%20she%20said.%20These%20companies%20would%20take%20away%20the%20passports%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20leave%2C%20and%20force%20them%20to%20work%2012%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20refused%20to%20do%20what%20is%20asked%20of%20him%2C%20he%20would%20be%20tortured%20by%20way%20of%20physical%20assaults%2C%20electric%20shocks%2C%20solitary%20confinement%2C%20etc.%20Many%20Indians%20not%20willing%20to%20engage%20in%20such%20scams%20are%20trapped%20there.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20identify%2C%20contact%2C%20and%20bring%20them%20back%20through%20proper%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Padhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scammers%20would%20pose%20as%20women%20on%20dating%20apps%20and%20chat%20with%20the%20potential%20targets.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20some%20time%2C%20they%20would%20convince%20the%20target%20to%20invest%20in%20cryptocurrency%20trading.%20Many%20were%20duped%20in%20India%20this%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Rourkela%20Police%2C%20the%20agents%20got%20the%20men%20to%20join%20another%20company%20that%20focused%20on%20investment%20scams%20in%20October%202023.%20%26quot%3BThis%20company%20lured%20people%20to%20invest%20in%20fake%20stocks.%20They%20also%20created%20a%20fake%20online%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20gathered%20several%20key%20pieces%20of%20information%2C%20including%20the%20location%20of%20the%20fraud%20companies%2C%20their%20operatives%2C%20their%20modus%20operandi%2C%20and%20their%20management%20hierarchy%2C%20Ms%20Padhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20identified%20three%20high-level%20operatives%20of%20Indian%20origin%20and%20one%20high-level%20operative%20of%20Nepalese%20origin.%20%26quot%3BWe%20intend%20to%20arrest%20key%20players%20in%20this%20scam%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Interpol%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711873380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fi34b21a8_cyber-crime-generic-reuters_625x300_31_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffake-profiles-pics-how-indians-in-cambodia-were-forced-to-scam-indians-5344676%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%205%2C000%20Indians%20are%20being%20reportedly%20held%20against%20their%20will%20in%20Cambodia%20and%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20scam%20Indians%20back%20home%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22enga