d-of-dc-csk-clash%2Farticleshow%2F108915075.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20Shrugs%20Off%20Short-Seller's%20Effect%2C%20Back%20To%20Rapid%20Expansion%20Spree%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20opened%20a%20USD%201.2%20billion%20copper%20plant%2C%20bought%20a%20port%20in%20Odisha%2C%20raised%20stakes%20in%20a%20cement%20company%20and%20stitched%20an%20alliance%20with%20rival%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20all%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20one%20week%20in%20signs%20that%20the%20apples-to-airport%20conglomerate%20has%20shrugged%20off%20the%20Hindenburg%20effect%20and%20is%20back%20to%20rapid%20expansion%20spree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20one%20week%2C%20Adani%20Group%20has%20through%20regulatory%20filings%20and%20press%20statements%20announced%20expansions%20and%20investments%20in%20its%20mainstay%20ports%20business%2C%20diversification%20into%20metal%20refining%2C%20fund%20infusion%20into%20a%20two-year-old%20cement%20foray%20and%20continuing%20progress%20in%20the%20commissioning%20of%20its%20mega%20solar%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20the%20March%2026%20announcement%20of%20Adani%20Ports%20acquiring%20a%2095%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Gopalpur%20Port%20for%20Rs%203%2C350%20crore%2C%20taking%20the%20number%20of%20seaports%20under%20its%20control%20to%2015%20-%20the%20highest%20with%20any%20private%20firm%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20Adani%20Enterprises%20Ltd%20-%20the%20group's%20flagship%20firm%20and%20business%20incubator%20-%20announcing%20on%20March%2028%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20single-location%20copper%20manufacturing%20plant%20at%20Mundra%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20marking%20the%20conglomerate's%20foray%20into%20metals%20refining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USD%201.2%20billion%20(about%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore)%20plant%20helped%20India%20join%20China%20and%20other%20nations%20that%20are%20rapidly%20expanding%20production%20of%20copper%2C%20a%20metal%20crucial%20for%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%20Technologies%20critical%20to%20the%20energy%20transition%20like%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20charging%20infrastructure%2C%20solar%20photovoltaics%20(PV)%2C%20wind%20and%20batteries%2C%20all%20require%20copper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20group%20promoter%20Gautam%20Adani%20and%20his%20family%20invested%20Rs%206%2C661%20crore%20in%20Ambuja%20Cements%20to%20raise%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20country's%20second-largest%20cement%20company%20to%2066.7%20per%20cent%20as%20it%20looked%20well-positioned%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20country's%20infrastructure%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%20-%20the%20renewable%20energy%20arm%20of%20the%20group%20-%20announced%20the%20start%20of%20operation%20of%20its%20775-megawatt%20solar%20power%20projects%20in%20Khavda%2C%20Gujarat.%20Khavda%20is%20the%20site%20where%20it%20is%20building%20a%20vast%20solar%20farm%20to%20generate%2030%20gigawatts%20of%20electricity%20from%20solar%20rays%20as%20part%20of%20its%20plans%20to%20reach%2045%20GW%20capacity%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20happening%20on%20March%2028%20was%20Mr%20Adani%20and%20his%20often%20perceived%20rival%20billionaire%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20collaborating%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20when%20Reliance%20Industries%20picked%20up%20a%2026%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Adani%20Power's%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20power%20project%20for%20Rs%2050%20crore%20and%20signed%20a%20pact%20to%20use%20the%20plants'%20500%20MW%20of%20electricity%20for%20captive%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20businessmen%20hailing%20from%20Gujarat%20have%20often%20been%20pitted%20by%20media%20and%20commentators%20against%20each%20other%2C%20but%20they%20have%20for%20years%20tiptoed%20around%20each%20other%20to%20reach%20the%20top%20two%20rungs%20of%20Asia's%20wealth%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Mr%20Ambani's%20interests%20across%20oil%20and%20gas%20to%20retail%20and%20telecom%20and%20Mr%20Adani's%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20spanning%20seaports%20to%20airports%2C%20coal%20and%20mining%2C%20they%20rarely%20crossed%20each%20other's%20path%20except%20in%20the%20clean%20energy%20business%2C%20where%20the%20two%20have%20announced%20multi-billion%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20aspires%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20renewable%20energy%20producer%20by%202030%2C%20while%20Reliance%20is%20building%20four%20gigafactories%20at%20Jamnagar%20in%20Gujarat%20--%20one%20each%20for%20solar%20panels%2C%20batteries%2C%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20and%20fuel%20cells.%20Adani%20Group%20is%20also%20building%20three%20giga%20factories%20for%20manufacturing%20solar%20modules%2C%20wind%20turbines%20and%20hydrogen%20electrolysers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clash%20was%20also%20forecast%20when%20the%20Adani%20Group%20applied%20to%20participate%20in%20an%20auction%20of%20spectrum%20or%20airwaves%20capable%20of%20carrying%20fifth-generation%20(5G)%20data%20and%20voice%20services.%20However%2C%20unlike%20Mr%20Ambani%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20bought%20a%20400%20MHz%20spectrum%20in%20the%2026%20GHz%20band%2C%20which%20is%20not%20for%20public%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20two%20have%20been%20far%20from%20rivals.%20In%202022%2C%20a%20firm%20with%20erstwhile%20links%20to%20Mr%20Ambani%20sold%20its%20stake%20in%20news%20broadcaster%20NDTV%20to%20Mr%20Adani%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20takeover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcements%20in%20the%20last%20one%20week%20are%20signs%20that%20Mr%20Adani%20is%20back%20on%20an%20expansion%20spree%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20developments%20took%20place%2014%20months%20after%20Hindenburg%20Research%20accused%20the%20Adani%20Group%20of%20%26quot%3Bbrazen%20stock%20manipulation%26quot%3B%20and%20accounting%20fraud%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20stock%20market%20rout%20that%20erased%20about%20USD%20150%20billion%20in%20market%20value%20at%20its%20lowest%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rout%20in%20stock%20prices%20following%20the%20allegations%2C%20which%20the%20group%20denied%2C%20cost%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani%20his%20position%20as%20the%20world's%20second-richest%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20following%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20the%20conglomerate%20redrew%20its%20strategy%2C%20including%20trimming%20debt%20through%20prepayments%20and%20repayments%20of%20borrowings%2C%20paring%20the%20founder's%20share%20pledge%20and%20bringing%20in%20promoter%20and%20marquee%20investor%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20seems%20to%20be%20paying%20off%2C%20with%20the%20share%20prices%20of%20the%2010%20listed%20companies%20recovering%20all%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20revenues%20have%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20helping%20it%20reduce%20debt%2C%20meet%20financial%20obligations%2C%20boost%20stability%20and%20make%20strategic%20investments%20to%20further%20its%20growth%20and%20expansion%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20has%20raised%20over%20USD%205%20billion%20(Rs%2041%2C500%20crore)%20in%20equity%20and%20double%20of%20that%20in%20debt%20since%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStar%20investor%20GQG%20Partners%20bought%20stakes%20worth%20almost%20USD%204.3%20billion%20in%20five%20group%20companies%20between%20March%20and%20August%202023%2C%20while%20Qatar%20Investment%20Authority%20(QIA)%20and%20French%20energy%20giant%20TotalEnergies%20poured%20in%20USD%20770%20million%20in%20renewable%20energy%20firm%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%2C%20according%20to%20company%20filings%20and%20stock%20exchange%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParallelly%2C%20the%20promoters%20infused%20USD%204.6%20billion%20to%20repay%20loans%20against%20shares%2C%20servicing%20loans%20taken%20for%20cement%20acquisitions%20and%20supporting%20green%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20last%20week's%20announcement%2C%20it%20had%20been%20doing%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20(M%26amp%3BAs)%2C%20acquiring%20Sanghi%20cement%20for%20USD%20431%20million%2C%2049.38%20per%20cent%20in%20Indian%20Oil%20Tanking%20for%20USD%20128%20million%2C%20Karaikal%20port%20for%20USD%20181%20million%2C%20and%20Coastal%20Energen%20for%20USD%20420%20million%2C%20filing%20and%20stock%20exchange%20data%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20has%20planned%20a%20Rs%207%20lakh%20crore%20capital%20expenditure%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20for%20expanding%20its%20infrastructure%20business%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20investor%20presentation%20by%20the%20company%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711871160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fpgffti9_adani-group_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fadani-group-shrugs-off-short-sellers-effect-back-to-rapid-expansion-spree-5344497%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adani%20group%20opened%20a%20USD%201.2%20billion%20copper%20plant%2C%20bought%20a%20port%20in%20Odisha%2C%20raised%20stakes%20in%20a%20cement%20company%20and%20stitched%20an%20alliance%20with%20rival%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20all%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20one%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fadani-group-shrugs-off-short-sellers-effect-back-to-rapid-expansion-spree-5344497%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI's%20rate%20decisi