0unaccounted%20cash%20accounted.%20Therefore%2C%20this%20common%20man's%20predicament%20really%20stirred%20me.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20had%20to%20dissent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conference%20heard%20addresses%20from%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Courts%20of%20Nepal%20and%20Pakistan%20Justices%20Sapana%20Pradhan%20Malla%20and%20Syed%20Mansoor%20Ali%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20Alok%20Aradh%20and%20NALSAR%20Chancellor%20Justice%20S%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20also%20spoke%20at%20the%20conference%2C%20a%20press%20release%20from%20NALSAR%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711863780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2F30s3phgc_bv-nagarathna-justice-nagarathna-justice-bv-nagarathna_625x300_26_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-nagarathna-explains-why-she-dissented-in-demonetisation-judgment-5343976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Judge%20BV%20Nagarathna%20has%20cautioned%20against%20instances%20of%20governors%20sitting%20indefinitely%20on%20bills%20passed%20by%20elected%20legislatures%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20case%20involving%20the%20Punjab%20Governor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-nagarathna-explains-why-she-dissented-in-demonetisation-judgment-5343976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Comedian%20Who%20Failed%20JEE%20Twice%20Shares%205%20Lessons%3A%20''Trials%20I%20Faced...''%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0IIT%20JEE%20(Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%93%20Joint%20Entrance%20Exam)%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%C2%A0toughest%20in%20the%20country%20which%20demands%20strategic%20planning%2C%20focused%20dedication%2C%20and%20a%20disciplined%20approach.%C2%A0Recently%2C%20a%C2%A0photo%20of%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%5C%22%3E17-year-old's%20gruelling%20schedule%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20JEE%20preparation%20went%20viral%2C%C2%A0shedding%20light%20on%20the%20dedication%20required%20to%20succeed%20in%20such%20competitive%20exams.%20Since%20then%2C%20many%20people%20have%20shared%20their%20thoughts%20and%20opinions%20on%20the%20exam%2C%20while%20reflecting%20on%20their%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%C2%A0stand-up%20comedian%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20X%20and%20revealed%20the%20lessons%20that%20he%20learnt%20after%20failing%20the%20JEE%20twice.%C2%A0Appurv%20Gupta%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20get%20into%20IIT%20%26amp%3B%20IIMs%20and%20started%20studying%20in%20a%20private%20college%20in%20NCR%2C%20with%20no%20scope%20of%20what%20he%20would%20do%20ahead.%C2%A0However%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20all%20the%20trials%20he%20faced%20shaped%20him%20into%20a%20stronger%20and%20more%20resilient%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''But%20through%20all%20the%20challenges%2C%20I%20learned%20some%20important%20lessons.%20It%20taught%20me%3A%201.%20To%20keep%20trying%20even%20when%20things%20didn't%20go%20my%20way.%202.%20Ways%20to%20move%20forward%20when%20my%20original%20plans%20didn't%20work%20out.%203.%20how%20to%20learn%20from%20my%20mistakes%20and%20grow%20stronger.%204.%20that%20putting%20in%20effort%20and%20staying%20committed%20pays%20off.%205.%20the%20importance%20of%20believing%20in%20myself%20and%20never%20giving%20up%2C''%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20failed%20in%20JEE%20twice.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDid%20not%20get%20into%20IIT%20%26amp%3B%20IIMs.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnStarted%20studying%20in%20a%20private%20college%20in%20NCR%2C%20with%20no%20scope%20of%20what%20I%20will%20do%20ahead.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEither%20to%20go%20for%20a%20Job%20or%20do%20an%20MBA%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20was%20brutal%2C%20but%20the%20trials%20I%20faced%20shaped%20me%20into%20a%20stronger%2C%20more%20resilient%20individual.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAll%20those%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJl55Rn7zw5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJl55Rn7zw5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20APPURV%20GUPTA%20(%40appurv_gupta)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fappurv_gupta%2Fstatus%2F1772842525327610307%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E''These%20lessons%20shaped%20me%20into%20who%20I%20am%20today%20%E2%80%93%20someone%20who%20doesn't%20give%20up%20easily%20and%20is%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20challenge%20head-on.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it's%20not%20about%20where%20you%20start%2C%20but%20how%20you%20choose%20to%20navigate%20the%20journey%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJEE%20is%20an%20engineering%20entrance%20examination%20conducted%20for%20admission%20to%20various%20engineering%20colleges%20in%20India.%20Candidates%20have%20to%20first%20qualify%20for%20JEE%20Mains%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20advanced%20level%20of%20the%20entrance%20exam%20(JEE%20Advanced).%20The%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20office%20mode.%20The%20first%20exam%20is%20held%20in%20January%20and%20the%20second%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711863540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fhnr46iv_appurv-gupta_625x300_31_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fcomedian-who-failed-jee-twice-shares-5-important-lessons-the-trials-i-faced-5343936%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20a