ne_21.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-drdo-chief-on-agni-5-mirv-gives-india-next-level-deterrence-capability-5220771%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Agni-5%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-praises-first-flight-test-of-agni-5-missile-with-multiple-independently-targetable-re-entry-vehicle-tech-5218481%5C%22%3Enuclear-capable%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20measuring%2017.5%20metres%20in%20length%2C%20weighing%2050%20tonnes%2C%20carrying%20a%20one-ton%20payload%2C%20and%20boasting%20a%20range%20exceeding%205%2C000%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20Agni%20means%20fire%2C%20and%20the%20test%20mission%20was%20dubbed%20'Divyastra'%2C%20meaning%20divine%20weapon.%20The%20test%20aims%20to%20bolster%20India's%20nuclear%20deterrence%20capability%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-mission-divyastra-single-missile-can-deploy-multiple-warheads-5218773%5C%22%3Eexemplifying%20the%20MIRV%20(multiple%20independently%20targetable%20re-entry%20vehicle)%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20entails%20launching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshare-vision-of-free-indo-pacific-region-us-on-indias-agni-5-mirv-test-5226910%5C%22%3Emultiple%20warheads%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20single%20missile%20to%20target%20multiple%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20missile%20can%20be%20configured%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20warheads%20and%20decoys%2C%20potentially%20confusing%20adversaries%20and%20diminishing%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagni-prime-5-points-on-missile-thats-going-to-boost-indias-nuclear-arsenal-4106998%5C%22%3EAnti-Ballistic%20Missile%20(ABM)%3C%2Fa%3E%20missions.%20Such%20capability%20is%20designed%20to%20overwhelm%20the%20adversary's%20ABM%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmission-divyastra-meet-the-woman-scientist-sheena-rani-behind-agni-5-missile-with-multiple-warheads-5224381%5C%22%3EMeet%20'Divya%20Putri'%2C%20Scientist%20Behind%20Agni-5%20Missile%20With%20Multiple%20Warheads%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20no%20expansionist%20aspirations%20and%20has%20never%20initiated%20aggression%20against%20any%20country.%20Nonetheless%2C%20it%20has%20faced%20numerous%20aggressions%20since%20gaining%20independence.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmission-divyastra-meet-the-woman-scientist-sheena-rani-behind-agni-5-missile-with-multiple-warheads-5224381%5C%22%3EThe%20MIRV%20capability%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20bolster%20the%20assurance%20level%20of%20India's%20deterrence%20posture%20in%20alignment%20with%20its%20no-first-use%20policy.%20It%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20India's%20indigenous%20missile%20development%20programme%2C%20crucial%20for%20addressing%20security%20concerns%20arising%20from%20hostile%20Chinese%20activities%20along%20the%20border%2C%20Pakistan's%20backing%20of%20terrorism%20in%20India%2C%20growing%20military%20collaboration%20between%20China%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20militarisation%20of%20the%20Tibet%20Autonomous%20Region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrajectory%20and%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agni-V%20MIRV%20missile%20system%2C%20comprising%20several%20complex%20technologies%2C%20was%20developed%20by%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20The%20journey%20was%20not%20without%20its%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountries%20possessing%20the%20most%20advanced%20missiles%20have%20often%20kept%20critical%20missile%20technologies%20within%20an%20exclusive%20club.%20While%20some%20have%20shared%20older-generation%20missile%20technologies%20with%20close%20allies%2C%20they%20have%20refrained%20from%20sharing%20niche%20missile%20technologies%20with%20advanced%20capabilities%2C%20even%20with%20closest%20allies.%20India%2C%20like%20many%20others%2C%20faced%20denials%20from%20this%20exclusive%20group%20of%20countries%20that%20possessed%20these%20advanced%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpiral%20Development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20leapfrogging%20and%20lean%20development%20philosophies%20hold%20relevance%2C%20development%2C%20testing%2C%20certification%2C%20and%20operationalisation%20of%20critical%20and%20complex%20technologies%20can%20be%20time-consuming%20and%20challenging.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20feasible%20to%20develop%20robust%20systems%20in%20the%20first%20attempt%2C%20thus%20necessitating%20a%20'spiral%20development'%20philosophy.%20The%20development%20of%20the%20advanced%2C%20versatile%2C%20accurate%2C%20and%20lethal%20Agni-5%20missile%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20systematic%20development%20approach%20involving%20diverse%20technologies%20and%20different%20variants%20of%20the%20Agni%20missile.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20long%2C%20arduous%2C%20and%20challenging%20journey%20marked%20by%20hard%20work%2C%20failures%2C%20and%20successes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conceptualisation%20of%20missile%20development%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20early%201980s%2C%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Integrated%20Guided%20Missile%20Development%20Program%20(IGMDP)%20in%201982-83%2C%20which%20set%20into%20motion%20a%20series%20of%20missile%20development%20programmes.%20The%20Agni-5%20MIRV%20test%20flight%20is%20the%20outcome%20of%20four%20decades%20of%20spiral%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20series%20of%20Agni%20series%20missiles%20were%20developed%20thus%2C%20including%20the%20first%20test%20of%20the%20two-stage%20Agni%20technology%20demonstrator%20in%201989%2C%20the%20700-1%2C250%20km%20range%20rail%2Froad%20mobile%20solid%20fuel%20Agni-1%20in%202002%2C%20the%202%2C000-2%2C500%20km%20Agni-II%2C%20the%203%2C000-3%2C500%20km%20range%20three-stage%20Agni-III%2C%20and%20the%203%2C000-4%2C000%20km%20range%20solid%20fuel%20propellant%20Intermediate%20Range%20Ballistic%20Missile%20Agni-IV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBallistic%20Missile%20Development%3A%20Agni-IV%20and%20Agni-V%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20the%20Agni-IV%20Intermediate-Range%20Ballistic%20Missile%20(IRBM)%20and%20the%20canister-launched%20three-stage%20Intercontinental%20Ballistic%20Missile%20(ICBM)%20Agni-V%20involved%20the%20indigenous%20development%20of%20several%20critical%20technologies%20in%20India.%20These%20advancements%20included%20the%20implementation%20of%20ring%20laser%20gyroscopes%2C%20composite%20rocket%20motors%2C%20launchers%2C%20and%20more.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20Circular%20Error%20of%20Probability%20(CEP)%20of%20these%20missiles%20was%20progressively%20reduced%20to%20enhance%20their%20accuracy%20and%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHandholding%20During%20Failures%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agni%20missile%20development%20programmes%20encountered%20numerous%20setbacks%20at%20different%20stages%2C%20stemming%20from%20technological%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20other%20flaws.%20Instances%20include%20the%20failed%20Agni-I%20missile%20test%20on%20May%2029%2C%201992%2C%20the%20unsuccessful%20testing%20of%20the%20Agni-III%20missile%20with%20a%20new%20rocket%20configuration%20on%20July%209%2C%202006%2C%20and%20the%20first-night%20user%20trial%20failure%20of%20the%20nuclear-capable%20Agni-II%20IRBM%20missile%20on%20November%2024%2C%202009%2C%20among%20others.%20Such%20setbacks%20are%20not%20unique%20to%20India%2C%20as%20similar%20challenges%20have%20been%20faced%20by%20the%20US%2C%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20other%20nations.%20Despite%20these%20obstacles%2C%20India%20persisted%20with%20the%20indigenous%20development%20of%20Agni%20missiles%2C%20demonstrating%20remarkable%20resilience%20during%20adversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20indigenous%20Agni%20MIRV%20programme%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20synergy%20among%20developers%2C%20users%2C%20and%20manufacturers.%20The%20development%20and%20testing%20of%20the%20Agni-V%20MIRV%20represent%20the%20initial%20steps%20toward%20operationalising%20this%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20past%20user%20flight%20trial%20failures%20underscore%20the%20complexities%20involved%20in%20transitioning%20from%20prototype%20to%20operational%20missile%20systems.%20Given%20China's%20advancement%20in%20MIRV%20technology%2C%20expediting%20the%20operationalisation%20and%20induction%20of%20the%20Agni-V%20MIRV%20is%20prudent.%20Additionally%2C%20India%20should%20continue%20its%20Agni-VI%20program%20to%20develop%20ICBMs%20with%20ranges%20exceeding%208%2C000%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELessons%20for%20India's%20UAV%20Programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20missile%20and%20UAV%20(unmanned%20aerial%20vehicle)%20development%20programmes%20share%20a%20common%20thread%20as%20both%20have%20been%20overseen%20by%20DRDO.%20Yet%2C%20their%20outcomes%20differ%20significantly.%20While%20the%20Agni%20programme%20successfully%20developed%20complex%20and%20denied%20technologies%2C%20yielding%20a%20series%20of%20indigenous%20Agni%20missiles%2C%20navigation%20systems%2C%20payloads%2C%20and%20critical%20subsystems%2C%20the%20progress%20of%20India's%20UAVs%20has%20been%20less%20successful%20thus%20far.%20In%20the%20tactical%20and%20Medium%20Altitude%20Long%20Endurance%20(MALE)%20UAV%20segment%2C%20projects%20such%20as%20Nishant%2C%20Panchi%2C%20Rustom-I%2C%20and%20Tapas%20have%20been%20undertaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20challenges%20such%20as%20vulnerability%20to%20satellite%20detection%20led%20to%20the%20abandoning%20of%20projects%20like%20Nishant%2C%20while%20others%20like%20Panchi%20faced%20discontinuation%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20further%20orders.%20Despite%20having%20been%20built%20from%20a%20successful%20manned%20aircraft%2C%20the%20future%20of%20Short-Range%20Unmanned%20Aerial%20Vehicles%20(SRUAV)%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tapas%20Medium%20Altitude%20Long%20Endurance%20(MALE)%20UAV%20development%20project%20was%20sanctioned%20in%202011%2C%20with%20its%20maiden%20flight%20occurring%20in%20November%202016.%20DRDO%20laboratories%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20developing%20numerous%20critical%20systems%20and%20sub-systems%20for%20Tapas%2C%20including%20the%20autopilot%2C%20communication%20systems%2C%20Automatic%20Takeoff%20and%20Landing%20(ATOL)%2C%20Ground%20Control%20System%20(GCS)%2C%20Synthetic%20Aperture%20Radar%20(SAR)%2C%20Medium%20Range%20Electro%20Optic%20(MREO)%2C%20and%20Indigenous%20Geo%20Augmented%20Navigation%20(GAGAN)%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20systems%20underwent%20testing%20on%20the%20Rustom-1%20platform%20before%20being%20integrated%20into%20Tapas%2C%20a%20significant%20achievement%20considering%20India's%20historical%20dependence%20on%20imports%20for%20critical%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDRDO%20has%20encountered%20challenges%20in%20developing%20tactical%20or%20MALE%20UAVs%20over%20the%20past%20three-and-a-half%20decades.%20Despite%20developing%20several%20crucial%20enabling%20technologies%2C%20India%20awaits%20the%20operationalisation%20and%20induction%20of%20indigenous%20UAVs.%20While%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Agni%20missile%20programme%20showcases%20the%20potential%20and%20capabilities%20of%20DRDO%20scientists%2C%20the%20not-so-remarkable%20journey%20in%20UAV%20development%20programmes%20necessitates%20introspection.%20The%20reasons%20behind%20failures%20in%20these%20UAV%20programmes%20must%20be%20thoroughly%20examined%2C%20and%20solutions%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20examination%20is%20needed%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20approach%20to%20handling%20failures%20in%20the%20Agni%20missile%20programme%20differs%20from%20that%20in%20indigenous%20UAV%20projects.%20Was%20the%20spiral%20development%20approach%2C%20successful%20in%20the%20missile%20program%2C%20adopted%20in%20UAV%20development%3F%20Was%20there%20synergy%20among%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20missile%20programme%2C%20different%20from%20UAV%20programmes%3F%20Were%20the%20approaches%20of%20DRDO%20teams%20or%20decision-makers%20different%20in%20missile%20programmes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20gaps%20and%20challenges%20of%20UAV%20programmes%20may%20differ%20from%20those%20of%20the%20Agni%20missile%20programme%2C%20they%20are%20surmountable%20and%20must%20be%20addressed.%20India's%20UAV%20programme%20stands%20at%20a%20crucial%20juncture%2C%20equipped%20with%20enabling%20technologies%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20success.%20It%20is%20passing%20through%20the%20Marut%20moment%3B%20the%20famous%20indigenous%20fighter%20development%20program%20of%20the%20early%201960s%20that%20could%20not%20be%20retrieved%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20perseverance%20and%20other%20challenges.%20Thorough%20analysis%20and%20suitable%20course%20corrections%20are%20necessary%20to%20realign%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DRDO's%20capabilities%2C%20demonstrated%20in%20the%20missile%20programme%2C%20must%20be%20replicated%20in%20the%20UAV%20projects.%20UAVs%2C%20like%20missiles%2C%20are%20pivotal%20to%20the%20future%20of%20aerial%20warfare%20and%20must%20be%20prioritised%20to%20meet%20India's%20security%20needs.%20The%20missile%20programme%20offers%20several%20lessons%20in%20that%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BGroup%20Captain%20(Dr.)%20R.K.%20Narang%2C%20Vayu%20Sena%20Medal%20(Retd.)%20is%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Manohar%20Parrikar%20Institute%20for%20Defence%20Studies%20and%20Analysis%20and%20a%20former%20IAF%20helicopter%20pilot.%C2%A0He%20associated%20with%20the%20Centre%20for%20Air%20Power%20Studies%20(CAPS)%2C%20was%20Director%2C%20Strategic%20Initiatives%20at%20the%20Drone%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20member%20of%20the%20Drone%20Working%20Sub%20Group%2C%20Department%20of%20Industry%20and%20Internal%20Trade%20(DPIIT)%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20and%20of%20High%20Power%20Steering%20Committee%20(HPSC)%20of%20Innovation%20for%20Defence%20Excellence%20(iDEX)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711861560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2F09t1v5m8_agni-prime-test-fired_625x300_28_June_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-indias-agni-5-missile-feat-lessons-to-overcome-unmanned-aerial-vehicles-stumbles-5343744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Agni%20missile%20programme%20showcases%20the%20potential%20and%20capabilities%20of%20DRDO%20scientists%2C%20the%20not-so-remarkable%20journey%20in%20UAV%20development%20programmes%20necessitates%20introspection.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-indias-agni-5-missile-feat-lessons-to-overcome-unmanned-aerial-vehicles-stumbles-5343744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Swatantra%20Veer%20Savarkar%20box%20office%20collection%20day%209%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711861544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108912149%2Cimgsize-26464.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fswatantra-veer-savarkar-box-office-collection-day-9-randeep-hooda-starrer-inches-towards-rs-15-crore%2Farticleshow%2F108912178.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108912178.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERandeep%20Hood