festation%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20in%20the%20maritime%20domain%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20corridor%20-%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20busiest%20cargo%20and%20oil%20transit%20points%20-%20since%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20responded%20to%20at%20least%2018%20incidents%20between%20December%202023%20and%20March%202024%20and%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20responder%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bpreferred%20security%20partner%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%2C%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20the%20Navy%20came%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20several%20nations%20as%20the%20menace%20of%20pirate%20attacks%20in%20this%20major%20trade%20route%20was%20compounded%20by%20drone%20and%20missile%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Navy%20Secured%20A%20Pirate%20Mother%20Ship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPirates%20hijacked%20a%20Malta-flagged%20cargo%20vessel%20with%20the%20call%20sign%20Ruen%20on%20December%2014%2C%202023.%20An%20SOS%20was%20sent%20out%20by%20the%20crew%20onboard%20and%20the%20Navy%20began%20tracking%20it%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20was%20indicated%20that%20six%20pirates%20had%20illegally%20boarded%20it%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20deployed%20a%20warship%20on%20anti-piracy%20patrol%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20to%20locate%20and%20assist%20the%20seized%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndianNavy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndianNavy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20manifestation%20of%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20Hamas%20conflict%20in%20the%20maritime%20domain%20by%20re-orienting%20%26amp%3B%20significantly%20enhancing%20the%20scope%20of%20its%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fmaritimesecurityoperations%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23maritimesecurityoperations%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20mid-Dec%2023.%20The%20navy%20undertook%20proactive%20actions%20during%20the%20hijacking%20of%20Malta%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fr5dNiW6PN4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fr5dNiW6PN4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20SpokespersonNavy%20(%40indiannavy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Findiannavy%2Fstatus%2F1771522408123646088%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20it%20was%20indicated%20that%20a%20crew%20of%20the%20vessel%20had%20been%20injured.%20The%20Navy%20launched%20a%20rescue%20op%20and%20evacuated%20the%20injured%20sailor%20from%20the%20vessel%20within%20four%20days.%20He%20was%20then%20flown%20to%20Oman%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20pirates%20overtook%20control%20of%20MV%20Ruen%20and%20steered%20it%20towards%20the%20Somalian%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20warships%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20the%20northern%20Arabian%20Sea%20to%20assist%20vessels%20east%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20where%20the%20navies%20of%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20secure%20the%20route%20from%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20hijacking%2C%20the%20Navy%20kept%20the%20region%20under%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%20surveillance%20activities%26quot%3B%2C%20using%20aerial%20platforms%20and%20other%20vessels%20to%20gather%20information%20and%20monitor%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20days%20and%20three%20months%20later%2C%20MV%20Ruen%20was%20spotted%20off%20the%20Somali%20coast%20on%20March%2014%2C%20information%20came%20in%20from%20the%20British%20maritime%20security%20firm%20Ambrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pirates%20converted%20the%20bulk%20carrier%20into%20a%20mothership%20to%20attack%20other%20ships.%20On%20March%2015%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20re-routed%20its%20warship%20INS%20Kolkata%20to%20intercept%20it.%20INS%20Kolkata%20sailed%20over%202%2C600%20km%20and%20cornered%20the%20vessel%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty%20hours%20later%2C%20the%20Navy%20forced%2035%20Somali%20pirates%20to%20surrender%20and%20rescued%2017%20crew%20members%20held%20hostage%20on%20the%20hijacked%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-stakes%20op%20involved%20multiple%20Navy%20vessels%2C%20drones%2C%20aircraft%2C%20and%20marine%20commandos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Subhadra%20-%20a%20patrol%20vessel%2C%20High%20Altitude%20Long%20Endurance%20(HALE%20RPA)%20drones%2C%20and%20P8I%20maritime%20patrol%20aircraft%20joined%20forces%20to%20help%20INS%20Kolkata%20take%20control%20of%20the%20pirate%20mother-ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20squad%20of%20eight%20marine%20commandos%20(MARCOS%20PRAHARs)%20were%20airdropped%20by%20a%20C-17%20aircraft%20onto%20the%20vessel%20to%20detain%20the%20pirates%20and%20safely%20evacuate%20the%20crew.%20No%20injuries%20were%20reported%20during%20the%20audacious%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavy%20To%20The%20Rescue%20Of%20Pakistani%20Nationals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20INS%20Kolkata's%20operation%2C%20the%20Navy%20rescued%2023%20Pakistani%20nationals%20from%20a%20hijacked%20Iranian%20fishing%20vessel%20%26quot%3BAl-Kambar%20786%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Sumedha%20intercepted%20the%20fishing%20vessel%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20March%2029%20and%20was%20subsequently%20joined%20by%20the%20guided%20missile%20frigate%20INS%20Trishul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndianNavy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndianNavy%3C%2Fa%3E%20Responds%20to%20Piracy%20Attack%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5