d%22%3A1711850280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6608c30016bde8d4ead3e7b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felf-cosmetics-corpse-paint-palette-goth-culture-appropriation-liquid-death-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22E.l.f.%20Cosmetics'%20new%20%26quot%3BCorpse%20Paint%26quot%3B%20palette%20has%20some%20goths%20on%20social%20media%20suggesting%20the%20brand%20appropriated%20their%20culture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A232%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felf-cosmetics-corpse-paint-palette-goth-culture-appropriation-liquid-death-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin%20Teen%20In%20UK%20Gets%20%26quot%3BLife-Changing%26quot%3B%20Cancer%20Treatment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYuvan%20Thakkar%2C%20an%20Indian-origin%20teenager%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%2C%20says%20he%20is%20now%20able%20to%20enjoy%20the%20things%20he%20loves%20after%20life-changing%20treatment%20thanks%20to%20a%20fund%20set%20up%20by%20the%20UK's%20state-funded%20National%20Health%20Service%20to%20make%20innovative%20therapies%20accessible%20to%20thousands%20of%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NHS%20England%2C%2016-year-old%20Mr%20Thakkar%20from%20Watford%20near%20London%20was%20the%20first%20child%20in%20the%20UK%20to%20benefit%20from%20a%20pioneering%20CAR%20T%20therapy%20called%20tisagenlecleucel%20(Kymriah)%20thanks%20to%20its%20Cancer%20Drugs%20Fund%20(CDF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20the%20National%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%20marks%20a%20milestone%20this%20weekend%20of%20100%2C000%20patients%20benefitting%20from%20early%20access%20to%20the%20latest%20and%20most%20innovative%20treatments%20with%20the%20help%20of%20CDF.%20The%20undisclosed%20cost%20of%20such%20treatments%20is%20covered%20by%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20life%20has%20changed%20so%20much%20since%20I%20received%20the%20CAR%20T%20therapy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Thakkar%2C%20who%20thanked%20Great%20Ormond%20Street%20Hospital%20(GOSH)%20in%20London%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bincredible%26quot%3B%20care%20he%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20I%20had%20to%20take%20so%20many%20trips%20to%20hospital%20and%20had%20long%20periods%20out%20of%20school...%20They%20have%20helped%20me%20recover%20to%20a%20state%20where%20I%20am%20able%20to%20enjoy%20so%20many%20things%20I%20love%20doing%2C%20such%20as%20playing%20snooker%20or%20pool%2C%20meeting%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20going%20on%20wonderful%20holidays.%20It's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20how%20things%20would%20have%20been%20if%20the%20treatment%20wasn't%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakkar%2C%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20form%20of%20leukaemia%20aged%20six%2C%20received%20a%20treatment%20which%20modifies%20a%20person's%20immune%20cells%20to%20recognise%20and%20attack%20cancer%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20treatment%20began%20in%202019%2C%20when%20he%20was%2011%20years%20old%20after%20he%20relapsed%20following%20other%20treatments%20such%20as%20chemotherapy%20and%20a%20bone%20marrow%20transplant.%20His%20mother%20Sapna%20said%20the%20family%20had%20received%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20chance%26quot%3B%20at%20life%20since%20the%20success%20of%20the%20treatment.%20Without%20the%20fast-track%20access%20available%20through%20the%20CDF%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20said%20there%20may%20have%20been%20no%20other%20way%20for%20her%20son%20to%20receive%20the%20life-saving%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20our%20prayers%20were%20finally%20answered.%20We%20still%20feel%20so%20grateful%20for%20this%20chance%20that's%20been%20given%20to%20us%20and%20not%20a%20single%20day%20passes%20by%20when%20we%20haven't%20felt%20thankful%20for%20all%20the%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20that%20have%20helped%20us%20through%20this%20long%20and%20difficult%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sapna%20Thakkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CDF%2C%20which%20opened%20in%20its%20current%20form%20in%20July%202016%2C%20is%20used%20by%20NHS%20England%20to%20provide%20fast-tracked%20access%20for%20patients%20to%20all%20new%20cancer%20treatments%20approved%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20for%20Health%20and%20Care%20Excellence%20(NICE)%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20gathering%20further%20evidence%20of%20long-term%20effectiveness%20for%20promising%20drugs.%20It%20allows%20faster%20access%20to%20more%20than%20100%20drugs%20to%20help%20improve%2C%20extend%20or%20-%20in%20some%20cases%20-%20save%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTreating%20100%2C000%20cancer%20patients%20in%20England%20with%20innovative%20treatments%20through%20the%20Cancer%20Drugs%20Fund%20is%20a%20fantastic%20milestone%20for%20the%20health%20service%20to%20reach%2C%20and%20testament%20to%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20oncologists%20and%20their%20teams%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Sir%20Stephen%20Powis%2C%20NHS%20national%20medical%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20vital%20fund%20is%20helping%20ensure%20patients%20get%20access%20to%20the%20most%20promising%20drugs%20far%20quicker%20than%20would%20otherwise%20be%20the%20case%2C%20helping%20people%20with%20cancer%20like%20Yuvan%20receive%20a%20life-changing%20intervention%20that%20sets%20a%20path%20for%20a%20longer%2C%20healthier%20life%20spent%20with%20family%20and%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20benefits%20people%20with%20common%20cancers%2C%20such%20as%20breast%2C%20lung%2C%20colorectal%20and%20prostate%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20with%20less%20common%20cancers%2C%20such%20as%20ovarian%2C%20cervical%2C%20kidney%2C%20skin%2C%20myeloma%2C%20lymphoma%20and%20leukaemia%2C%20and%20rare%20cancers%2C%20including%20thyroid%20and%20biliary%20tract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20CDF%20bud