I%20hope%20that%20judges%20will%20take%20this%20to%20heart.%20I%20know%20I%20have%20spoken%20with%20judges%20who've%20heard%20about%20the%20project%20and%20gone%20back%20to%20their%20clerks%20and%20said%2C%20'So%2C%20how%20do%20you%20feel%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-photos-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echamber's%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20How%20am%20I%20as%20a%20manager%3F%20How%20can%20I%20do%20better%3F'%26quot%3B%20Shatzman%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20important%20because%20absolutely%20everybody%20can%20improve.%20And%20this%20is%20a%20really%20important%20relationship%2C%20so%20it's%20important%20to%20get%20it%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-database-law-clerks-rate-boss-performance-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711833781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e532756080194819fc00b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-database-law-clerks-rate-boss-performance-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Creator%20Aliza%20Shatzman%20says%20the%20Legal%20Accountability%20Project%20database%20aims%20to%20diminish%20the%20culture%20of%20fear%20and%20silence%20surrounding%20the%20judiciary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-database-law-clerks-rate-boss-performance-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Americans%20are%20spending%20more%20on%20travel%20and%20live%20entertainment.%20But%20their%20personal%20saving%20rate%20has%20taken%20a%20dip.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22majorca%20spain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d7155436f24eb152934c0c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMajorca%20has%20beautiful%20limestone%20mountains%20and%20lots%20of%20hidden%20coves.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmericans%20are%20spending%20more%20on%20experiences%2C%20which%20they%20were%20largely%20deprived%20of%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConsumer%20spending%20on%20foreign%20trips%20and%20live%20entertainment%20rose%20by%20nearly%2030%25%20in%202023%2C%20WaPo%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20personal%20saving%20rate%20in%20the%20US%20has%20declined%2C%20falling%20to%203.6%25%20in%20February.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20earliest%20stages%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20many%20Americans%20reminisced%20about%20the%20things%20that%20used%20to%20bring%20them%20joy.%20They%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-covid-19-pandemic-reshaped-how-we-travel-forever-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20stopped%20thinking%20about%20that%20last%20big%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20their%20families%20or%20that%20last%20in-person%20concert%20they%20enjoyed%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20later%2C%20American%20consumers%20have%20mostly%20moved%20on%20from%20the%20pandemic%20and%20are%20spending%20more%20on%20experiences%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrioritizing%20experiences%2C%20however%2C%20has%20led%20to%20a%20major%20shift%20in%20their%20financial%20lives%3A%20The%20personal%20saving%20rate%20in%20the%20US%20has%20declined%20considerably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20recently%20reported%20on%20how%20consumers%20in%20the%20US%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2F03%2F29%2Fconsumer-spending-savings-yolo-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eembraced%20a%20sort%20of%20YOLO%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%26quot%3Byou%20only%20live%20once%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20mindset.%20In%202023%2C%20consumer%20spending%20on%20foreign%20trips%20and%20live%20entertainment%20rose%20by%20nearly%2030%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpending%20levels%20have%20so%20far%20continued%20to%20rise%20in%202024%2C%20too.%20In%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bea.gov%2Fnews%2F2024%2Fpersonal-income-and-outlays-february-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20consumption%20expenditures%20increased%20by%20%24145.5%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20to%20January%2C%20with%20%24111.8%20billion%20spent%20on%20services%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20perhaps%20predictably%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bea.gov%2Fdata%2Fincome-saving%2Fpersonal-saving-rate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%20personal%20saving%20rate%20has%20declined%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20bureau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20personal%20saving%20rate%20was%203.6%20percent%2C%20a%20drop%20from%204.1%20percent%20the%20month%20before.%20(The%20rate%20sat%20at%204%20percent%20last%20November%20and%203.9%20percent%20in%20December.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20consumers%20were%20able%20to%20spend%20freely%20on%20their%20wish%20list%20trips%20and%20attend%20concerts%20and%20festivals%20without%20onerous%20health%20restrictions%2C%20they%20started%20booking%20flights%20and%20hotel%20rooms%20and%20purchasing%20tickets%20to%20see%20the%20artists%20that%20they%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20instead%20of%20continuing%20to%20put%20away%20money%20for%20the%20future%2C%20which%20is%20what%20many%20people%20tried%20to%20do%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20many%20consumers%20now%20want%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20time%20they%20lost%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20live%20through%20a%20crisis%2C%20it%20gets%20ingrained%20in%20your%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20University%20of%20California%20at%20Berkeley%20behavioral%20finance%20professor%20Ulrike%20Malmendier%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post.%20%26quot%3BThe%20official%20economic%20reports%20might%20say%20everything%20is%20coming%20back%20to%20normal%2C%20but%20we%20are%20different%20people%20than%20we%20were%20before%20the%20pandemic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalmendier%20told%20the%20Post%20that%20after%20the%20Great%20Recession%2C%20many%20Americans%20overhauled%20their%20financial%20habits%3B%20many%20consumers%20started%20to%20save%20more%20of%20their%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20angst%20of%20Americans%20during%20the%20pandemic%20unleashed%20a%20different%20sort%20of%20sentiment%2C%20Malmendier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20adverse%20effects%20of%20Covid%20weren't%20necessarily%20financial%3B%20people%20got%20jobs%20quickly%20and%20the%20government%20stepped%20in%20with%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20it's%20about%20all%20of%20the%20things%20we%20were%20starved%20for%3A%20human%20interaction%2C%20socializing%2C%20travel.%20People%20are%20spending%20money%20on%20the%20things%20they%20missed%20most.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-consumer-spending-international-travel-entertainment-surge-savings-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711833471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66087d193f923f7dab02e901%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-consumer-spending-international-travel-entertainment-surge-savings-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202023%2C%20consumer%20spending%20on%20international%20trips%20and%20live%20entertainment%20rose%20by%20nearly%2030%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%2