imalaica%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20itself%20is%20in%20no%20way%20less%20captivating%20than%20the%20beauty%20around%20it.%20Made%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20blends%20into%20nature%20instead%20of%20standing%20out%20as%20a%20sore%20thumb%2C%20Varun%20explains%20their%20inspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20buildings%20are%20inspired%20by%20the%20various%20Chalets%20that%20we%20visited%20in%20Switzerland.%20We%20used%20stones%20from%20the%20Kolar%20River%20nearby%20to%20make%20the%20structure.%20The%20design%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20chalets%20and%20British%20villas%20that%20we%20have%20in%20Europe.%20The%20windows%20and%20the%20doors%20are%20all%20inspired%20by%20those%20designs%20while%20using%20the%20local%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98mini-castle%E2%80%99%20hidden%20in%20the%20woods.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20factor%20while%20designing%20the%20place%20was%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20as%20close%20to%20nature%20as%20possible.%20The%20place%2C%20despite%20being%20close%20to%20Nainital%2C%20feels%20like%20we%20are%20living%20in%20the%20old%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20retreat%20offers%20global%20cuisines%20to%20their%20guests.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345626%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20retreat%20offers%20global%20cuisines%20to%20their%20guests.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20already%20tried%20to%20incorporate%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20area%20into%20their%20homestay.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20Kumaoni%20art%20hung%20in%20the%20place%20to%20give%20the%20guests%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20culture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIte%20brought%20handlooms%20and%20pieces%20of%20art%20from%20Kashmir%20to%20make%20the%20place%20a%20hub%20of%20different%20cultures%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20place%20was%20our%20stepping%20stone%20to%20return%20home%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20place%20feels%20like%20one%20to%20us.%20Including%20elements%20of%20both%20our%20cultures%20and%20the%20design%20of%20the%20place%20we%20called%20home%20for%20so%20long%20in%20Switzerland%20was%20quite%20important%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20various%20activities%20that%20they%20provide%2C%20Ite%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20about%20three%20trekking%20routes%20that%20we%20encourage%20our%20guests%20to%20take.%20We%20also%20recommend%20exploring%20the%20area%20and%20exploring%20the%20Bhowali%20range.%20The%20guests%20can%20also%20engage%20in%20bird%20watching%20as%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F175950%2Findia-padma-shri-anup-sah-photography-himalayas-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20place%20is%20full%20of%20Himalayan%3C%2Fa%3E%20birds%20visiting%20the%20estate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20150%20species%20of%20birds%20are%20found%20in%20the%20area%2C%20sh