s%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Avarekalu%20uppittu%20(Rava-based%20upma%20using%20hyacinth%20beans).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAvarekalu%20uppittu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rava-based%20%3Cem%3Eupma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eusing%20hyacinth%20beans).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20the%20magic%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20to%20the%20Indian%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20inception%20%5Bof%20Adukale%5D%2C%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20watch%20my%20parents%20and%20aunt%20bring%20in%20their%20entrepreneurial%20prowess%20and%20passion%20to%20the%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20a%20few%20years%20after%20establishing%20Adukale%2C%20demand%20for%20their%20products%20grew%20so%20extensively%20in%20Bengaluru%20through%20just%20word%20of%20mouth%20that%20they%20were%20compelled%20to%20move%20away%20from%20their%20small%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20in%20Malathi%E2%80%99s%20home%20to%20a%203%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%2030%20tonnes.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20venture%20shifted%20to%20an%20even%20larger%207%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20in%20South%20Bengaluru%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20100%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20capacity%20growing%20multi-fold%2C%20their%20processes%20didn%E2%80%99t%20change.%20One%20of%20the%20three%20founding%20partners%20of%20the%20business%20continued%20to%20supervise%20each%20stage%20of%20production%20to%20ensure%20product%20quality%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wane.%20What%20also%20helped%20was%20Bharat%20joining%20the%20business%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWitnessing%20great%20promise%20in%20the%20venture%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20profession%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%20the%20US%20to%20join%20Adukale.%20As%20someone%20passionate%20about%20food%20and%20the%20culinary%20landscape%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20bring%20in%20my%20global%20experience%20and%20innovation%20to%20scale%20the%20brand%20and%20make%20strides%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235046%2Fbengaluru-woman-spices-entrepreneur-coffee-sambar-powder-natural-traditional-recipes-small-biz-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebringing%20regional%20food%20to%20the%20global%20map%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20an%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Old%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20an%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Old%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20does%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20brand%20necessitate%20breaking%20away%20from%20your%20Sankethi%20roots%20on%20the%20odd%20occasion%3F%20Bharat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20agree%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAdukale%20has%20always%20been%20a%20Karnataka%20brand%3B%20our%20roots%20are%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20the%20culinary%20heritage%20of%20the%20region.%20Similar%20to%20national%20brands%2C%20our%20products%20have%20their%20own%20USP%20%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20growth%20factor%20in%20the%20markets%20we%20operate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20world%20is%20our%20platter%20and%20cross-border%20integration%20of%20food%20has%20never%20been%20better.%20People%20thrive%20on%20homegrown%20recipes%20and%20products%20that%20are%20a%20window%20to%20different%20cultures.%20Given%20this%20background%2C%20our%20core%20will%20always%20remain%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20Adukale%20in%202017%2C%20Bharat%20became%20director%20in%202019%2C%20and%20subsequently%20the%20CEO%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Adukale%20enjoys%20an%20extensive%20selection%20of%2056%20products%2C%20available%20across%2020%20stores%20throughout%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mysuru.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20established%20a%20strong%20online%20presence%2C%20ensuring%20our%20offerings%20are%20accessible%20to%20customers%20far%20and%20wide.%20As%20Adukale%20continues%20to%20grow%20and%20expand%20its%20reach%2C%20it%20remains%20rooted%20in