w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-1-1711519971-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-1-1711519971-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAlongside%20cultivating%20vegetables%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20maize%2C%20Kanchan%20sowed%20turmeric%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202020.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOld%20field%2C%20new%20crop%2C%20huge%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20an%20agricultural%20background%2C%20Kanchan%20turned%20to%20farming%20soon%20after%20her%20marriage.%20Alongside%20cultivating%20vegetables%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20maize%2C%20the%20BA%20graduate%20sowed%20turmeric%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20programme%20on%20television%20that%20showcased%20the%20advantages%20of%20taking%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274975%2Fdivine-foods-helps-organic-turmeric-farmers-earn-double-sell-to-us-uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturmeric%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20learn%20more%20about%20it%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20nearby%20KVK%20(Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra)%20and%20undertook%20a%20training%20programme%20of%20seven%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanchan%20opted%20for%20the%20Sangli%20variety%20of%20turmeric%20which%20has%20high%20curcumin%20turmeric%20and%20is%20often%20used%20for%20medicinal%20purposes.%20In%20addition%20to%20its%20deep-orange%20colour%20and%20rich%20aroma%2C%20Kanchan%20says%2C%20this%20variety%20produces%20big%20roots%20compared%20to%20other%20indigenous%20varieties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20procured%20eight%20quintals%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekachhi%20haldi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(seed)%20from%20KVK%20at