%20not%20well-received%20by%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Indian%20households%20for%20the%20relatives%20to%20have%20strong%20opinions.%20My%20father%20was%20told%20that%20he%20has%20put%20so%20much%20money%20into%20our%20education%20and%20sent%20us%20abroad%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisheartened%20by%20the%20reaction%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%20that%20gave%20them%20the%20courage.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20told%20us%20that%20we%20need%20not%20listen%20to%20anyone.%20If%20this%20feels%20right%2C%20then%20we%20must%20continue%20with%20the%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20nod%20from%20his%20parents%2C%20the%20brother%20duo%20decided%20to%20use%20some%20savings%20and%20loan%20some%20amount%20to%20set%20up%20the%20polyhouse%20farm%20in%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%2C%20natural%20and%20fresh%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20the%20duo%20had%20initiated%20the%20setup%20of%20their%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20secured%20a%2040%20percent%20government%20subsidy%2C%20prompting%20us%20to%20commence%20with%20planting%20English%20Cucumber%20in%20our%20polyhouse%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20four%20months%2C%20the%20duo%20established%20their%20initial%20cultivation%20and%20harvested%20it%20within%20five%20months.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cucumber%20marked%20just%20the%20beginning.%20We%20sought%20further%20expansion%20and%20ventured%20into%20experimenting%20with%20additional%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Ayush%20recalls%2C%20while%20he%20was%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20small%20mushroom%20business.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sourced%20mushrooms%20from%20farmers%2C%20packed%20them%2C%20and%20sold%20them.%20Although%20brief%2C%20it%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20substantial%20profit%20potential%20of%20mushrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C