vious%20mushroom%20experience%2C%20Ayush%20also%20observed%20a%20trend%20in%20his%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20region%20is%20predominantly%20inhabited%20by%20vegetarians%20who%20favour%20mushrooms.%20Button%20mushroom%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20has%20surged%20over%20the%20years.%20With%20new%20recipes%20circulating%20online%2C%20people%20are%20relishing%20this%20chewy%20fungus.%20I%20even%20noticed%20mushrooms%20featuring%20prominently%20in%20wedding%20celebrations%2C%20with%20various%20dishes%20showcasing%20them%20as%20the%20main%20ingredient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20they%20yield%20approximately%2040%20tonnes%20of%20mushrooms%20per%20month.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20all%20A-grade%20mushrooms%2C%20distinguished%20by%20their%20maturity%2C%20well-formed%20shape%2C%20and%20meticulous%20trimming.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20are%20%E2%80%98B%E2%80%99%20grade%20mushrooms%2C%20which%2C%20due%20to%20irregular%20shapes%2C%20are%20sold%20to%20food%20processing%20companies%20for%20canning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOperating%20under%20the%20brand%20names%20Gupta%20Organic%20Farms%20and%20A3R%20Mushroom%20Farms%2C%20the%20brothers%20market%20their%20products%20to%20businesses%20and%20direct%20consumers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20supply%20to%20numerous%20businesses%20in%20Agra%20and%20Delhi%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20significant%20consumer%20demand%20in%20the%20city.%20In%20total%2C%20our%20monthly%20sales%20exceed%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Our%20annual%20turnover%20stands%20at%20Rs%207.5%20crores%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyush%20underscores%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20providing%20the%20best%20to%20its%20customers%2C%20emphasising%20that%20no%20chemicals%20are%20used%20to%20aid%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20vegetables%20and%20mushrooms%20are%20grown%20organically%2C%20without%20the%20use%20of%20any%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Ci