ia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20Gupta%20from%20Agra%20were%20studying%20abroad%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20disrupted%20their%20lives.%20The%20duo%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20home%20and%20started%20A3R%20Mushroom%20Farms%20and%20Gupta%20Organic%20Farms%2C%20growing%2040%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20mushrooms%20every%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344839%2Fhow-to-start-mushroom-business-agra-brothers-ayush-and-rishabh-gupta-earn-crores-from-organic-mushrooms%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20Brilliant%20Woman%20is%20Using%20Eco-Tourism%20to%20Help%20100s%20in%20Rural%20India%20Increase%20their%20Incomes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20fisherwoman%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shweta%20Hule%20tells%20me%2C%20her%20voice%20crisp%20and%20urgent.%20My%20first%20guess%20is%20that%20I%20am%20delaying%20her%20from%20commencing%20her%20day%E2%80%99s%20work.%20But%2C%20as%20she%20explains%2C%20fishing%20is%20not%20on%20the%20agenda%20today.%20She%20is%20taking%20a%20group%20of%20tourists%20for%20a%20boating%20ride%20through%20the%20Mandavi%20Creek%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sindhudurg.%20This%20is%20a%20welcome%20change%20in%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F227428%2Finland-fish-earnings-how-to-farming-rural-economy-livelihood-microentrepreneurs-ngo-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efisher%20folk%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20area%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20Hule%E2%80%99s%20day%20would%20be%20spent%20casting%20her%20net%20into%20the%20water.%20But%2C%20on%20the%20way%20back%2C%20she%20and%20the%20other%20fisher%20folk%20would%20allow%20themselves%20a%20short%20break%20during%20which%20they%20would%20sit%20back%20in%20thei