betterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-1-1710941612-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345348%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaurang%20Motta%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Monks%20Bouffe%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20much%20attention%20was%20paid%20to%20the%20community%20anyway%2C%20but%20what%20truly%20saddened%20us%20was%20witnessing%20the%20dying%20art%20without%20recognition.%20The%20community%20used%20handpicked%20flowers%20to%20create%20natural%20colours%20devoid%20of%20adulterants%2C%20a%20practice%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%20It%20was%20imperative%20for%20us%20to%20help%20preserve%20it.%20The%20younger%20generation%20of%20the%20tribe%20showed%20little%20interest%20in%20learning%20the%20art%20since%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20monetary%20gains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20salvage%20the%20art%2C%20the%20brothers%20initiated%20an%20annual%20project%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F174570%2Flifestyle-holi-organic-colours-make-at-home-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducing%20Holi%20colours%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20the%20tribe%20and%20selling%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20concept%20of%20natural%20colours%20was%20gaining%20traction%20at%20the%20time.%20We%20first%20launched%20the%20Holi%20colours%20in%202018%20and%20have%20been%20receiving%20more%20orders%20ever%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313885%2Fhyderabad-manya-cherabuddi-makes-natural-dyes-conducts-workshops-sustainable-living%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20colour-making%20process%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gaurang%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20colours%20are%20entirely%20natural%20and%20made%20from%20edible%20materials.%20The%20base%20is%20maize%20flour%20cultivated%20by%20the%20community%20itself.%20The%20orange%20colour%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20Palash%20flower%2C%20abundant%20in%20the%20area%20during%20March%20and%20April.%20Our%20yellow%20hue%20combines%20Palash%20flowers%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20turmeric.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreen%20hues%20are%20concocted%20from%20a%20blend%20of%20various%20forest%20leaves.%20%E2%80%9CLastly%2C%20we%20have%20a%20pink%20shade%20crafted%20using%20Ganganagri%20Rose%20along%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20dried%20beetroot%2C%20which%20enhances%20the%20vibrancy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flowers%20are%20first%20picked%2C%20sorted%20and%20cleaned.%20The%20ingredients%20are%20boiled%20for%2014-15%20minutes%20and%20then%20they%20are%20sieved%20to%20segregate%20the%20residue.%20Once%20this%20is%20done%2C%20the%20mixture%20is%20dried%20and%20then%20hand-pounded.%20This%20is%20then%20added%20to%20the%20organic%20maize%20flour%20to%20make%20natural%20colours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20primarily%20serves%20customers%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%20a%20few%20others%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20along%20with%20numerous%20wholesale%20partners%20who%20sell%20these%20products%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20retail%20through%20our%20website%20and%20Amazon%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tribals%20handmade%20all%20the%20colours%20using%20flowers%20like%20Palash%20and%20Ganaganagri%20Rose.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03